org.ldaptive.ldapi

Class AFUnixSocketFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.net.SocketFactory
      • org.ldaptive.ldapi.AFUnixSocketFactory

  • public class AFUnixSocketFactory
extends SocketFactory
    AFUnixSocketFactory is an extension of SocketFactory which utilizes AFUNIXSocket to connect to a host, it is intended for local file-based native socket connections only.

    • Field Summary
